.
In [151]:
def select_sort(arr):
    # ,
    for i in range(0, len(arr)):
        # 
        index = np.argmin(arr[i:]) + i 
        if arr[i] > arr[index]:
            # 
            arr[i], arr[index] = arr[index], arr[i]
    return arr
